===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An owl of the genus ''{{l|mul|Bubo}}'' native to the Americas, among the largest types of owl, having two horn-like tufts of feathers on its head.

====Usage notes====
The Eurasian species of ''Bubo'' are called [[eagle owl|eagle owls]]. The Arctic [[snowy owl]] is found both in the Old and the New World.

